===============================================================================
  nightly.xml for Nightly Builds
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Requires Java 1.6+ and Apache Ant 1.7.1

1.) Download nightly.xml to an empty directory (via svn export, curl, wget, etc.)
        https://smartbody.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/smartbody/trunk/build/nightly.xml
2.) Set Java VM memory parameters for Ant
        set ANT_OPTS=-xms512m -Xmx1g
3.) Run Ant
        ant -buildfile nightly.xml


Configurable Build Parameters
-----------------------------

svn.password
    If set, and build is successful, the system will attempt tag the build in SVN repository,
    using the build report as the commit message.

